author: The Current
description:
Gillian Welch describes a guitar that has been her mainstay since 1996.
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

Following a session in The Current studio, singer-songwriter Gillian Welch talked about how a guitar she bought just after she released her first album has been her touring mainstay ever since. 

Find more here: https://www.thecurrent.org/feature/2025/03/03/the-current-guitar-collection-gillian-welch-1956-gibson-j50
